  "title": "Celeriac and Apple Soup",
  "subtitle": "A blended soup, smooth and warm.",
  "excerpt": "Celeriac and Apple Soup. A smooth blended soup with simple components, vegetables sweated low, stock added, blitzed at the end.",
  "type": "RECIPE",
