    "content": [
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Celeriac and Apple Soup. A British home-cook's dish, the kind of recipe families adjust across generations. Serves 4.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "A blended soup in the everyday register: vegetables sweated low, stock added, blitzed until smooth. The work is the dicing; everything else is patience.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
